{
  "title": "Intensely Savory Italian Chicken Liver Caponata",
  "description": "A cultured and adventurous Sardinian dish featuring chicken liver, served with double-rise-bread, this caponata is a perfect blend of savory flavors, and is fodmap-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
